name: catch the food (deadbrain.games)
description:
This game was originally made for mini jam 80

A 2D infinite runner side scrolling platform where you play as hungry cat. Can you keep a balanced diet?

This is an open-source game which can be found at https://code.deadbrain.games/catch-the-food.git

The game was made using free assets (mostly from other itch.io users):

  • font: Silverfinster Font by heaven castro
  • music: Smooth Sailing by DOS-88
  • sound fx: GAMEBOY SFX PACK #1 by OmegaPixelArt
